claim.claim-text:
An analyzing device having a plurality of maintenance items, comprising:
storage means configured to store recommended intervals for performing the maintenance for each of the maintenance items;
extracting means configured to extract maintenance items to be performed on the basis of the intervals of performance of the maintenance stored in the storage means upon reception of an instruction to perform the maintenance at a time point when the instruction is issued;
sorting means configured to sort the maintenance items extracted by the extracting means in the order of performance of the maintenance on the basis of a predetermined rule; and
display means configured to display the maintenance items in the order sorted by the sorting means.

A management system for an analyzing device comprising:
an analyzing device having a plurality of maintenance items;
storage means configured to store recommended intervals for performing the maintenance for each of the maintenance items;
extracting means configured to extract maintenance items to be performed on the basis of the intervals of performance of the maintenance stored in the storage means upon reception of an instruction to perform the maintenance at a time point when the instruction is issued;
sorting means configured to sort the maintenance items extracted by the extracting means in the order of performance of the maintenance on the basis of a predetermined rule;
display means configured to display the maintenance items in the order sorted by the sorting means.

A management method for an analyzing device comprising:
a storage step for storing recommended intervals for performing the maintenance for each of the maintenance items of an analyzing device having a plurality of maintenance items;
an extracting step for extracting maintenance items to be performed on the basis of the intervals of performance of the maintenance stored in the storage step upon reception of an instruction to perform the maintenance at a time point when the instruction is issued;
a sorting step for sorting the maintenance items extracted in the extracting step in the order of performance of the maintenance on the basis of a predetermined rule; and
a displaying step for displaying the maintenance items in the order sorted in the sorting step.
